high_descs: Turn left move forward on the table
Pick up the potato beside the coffee maker
Turn left move forward, then right head to the sink
Put the potato in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the potato turn left move forward then turn right head to the trash bin
Put the potato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the clean potato in the trash bin

high_descs: Walk over to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden table.
Pick up the potato off of the wooden table.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean potato.
Turn around and walk to the door, then hang a right and walk over to the white bin that is to the left of the counter.
Put the clean potato in the small white bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in a white bin.

high_descs: turn to the left and move to the round table
pick up the potato off of the round table
turn left and move forward across the room to the sink
put the potato in to the sink, turn on the water to clean the potato, turn off the water and remove the potato from the sink
turn around and move forward to the end of the kitchen to the trash can on the right side in the corner
put the potato in to the trash can
anns.task_desc: put a clean potato in to the trash can
